to add a level click add file at the top of the data tab
then name that new file "SampleLevel#.json" (has to be exact and replace "#" with a free number
then copy the code from another sample level (presumably one with no victors)
paste it into the new file and change the name and other data of the level
author is the account it was published on
creator is the account that made it
and verifier is obvious
once you do that, go to list.json and the order of them from top to bottom are in difficulty (top being hardest while bottom is easiest)
then put the name of the file ("SampleLevel#.json") where it should be on the list then add a comma after the ""
if the level is at the bottom then dont add a comma
                                                                                              
!!!! make sure you save after editing a file !!!!

if you need further help just ask!!!!!!
list shoukd update on its own
and if a level is yet to be added but you dont want it to be put on the list without warning, dont add it to list.json
